#Learning Django

If you're here, it’s likely because you’re interested in learning Django. This powerful web framework is fantastic for building robust and scalable web applications.

I’m documenting my journey to learn Django. I’ll be sharing insights, tips, and recommendations on how to master Django, starting from the basics.

Also, I’m doing this because I tend to forget how I learned things later on.

Stage 1: 
Let’s begin by exploring some free resources in Django.
